		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Denine wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Maybe add some "Continue"?</div>
<br />
<br />Nah, the game is finished as is. I spent a lot of time with my testers trying to find a good balance to the levels. I think it was accomplished. Though it might seem hard at first, it's not all that bad really. Don't forget that you have a teleporter at your disposal! I couldn't beat it when I first started playing, but now I have some strategic spots where I lay the teleporter that really help a bunch : )

		

